{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "course-center-api-collection",
		"name": "课程中心 API Collection",
		"description": "完整的课程中心后端API测试集合 - 包含24个接口\n\n## 模块说明\n- 认证模块: 5个接口（注册、登录、获取用户信息、更新信息、修改密码）\n- 课程模块: 13个接口（列表、详情、筛选、搜索、推荐、热门、最新、章节、报名、收藏、进度等）\n- 分类模块: 2个接口（分类列表、分类详情）\n- 讲师模块: 1个接口（明星讲师）\n- 评价模块: 4个接口（评价列表、添加、更新、删除）\n\n## 使用说明\n1. 先执行「用户登录」接口获取Token\n2. Token会自动保存到环境变量中\n3. 需要认证的接口会自动使用保存的Token\n4. 可根据需要修改base_url变量",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "认证模块",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "用户注册",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"user_name\": \"测试用户\",\n  \"phone\": \"13900000000\",\n  \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "用户登录",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (response.success && response.data.token) {",
									"        pm.environment.set('token', response.data.token);",
									"        console.log('Token已保存:', response.data.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"13900139001\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "获取当前用户信息",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "me"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "更新用户信息",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"user_name\": \"张三\",\n  \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",\n  \"occupation\": \"软件工程师\",\n  \"learning_goal\": \"提升技术能力\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/profile",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "profile"]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "修改密码",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"oldPassword\": \"123456\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"654321\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/password",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "password"]
						}
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
